											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Ketheric stands up quickly, hatred in his eyes. Gestures to cast a big, scary looking necro spell aimed at the player. The player shields themselves, but at the moment where it seems Ketheric is about to launch a fatal blow, a flash of light appears, and Ketheric is pushed away and to the ground. Nightsong is standing in his place." />
